ption":"气的生理功能包括推动作用、温煦作用、防御作用、固摄作用和气化作用。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggswj_ay_2253_201407","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"E","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"温煦作用","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"防御作用","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"运化作用","fourth":"固摄作用","answerPic":"","first":"推动作用"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"下列哪项不是气的组成","discription":"气可分为元气、宗气、营气和卫气四种。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggswj_ay_2254_201407","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"C","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"宗气","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"胃气","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"卫气","fourth":"营气","answerPic":"","first":"元气"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"风邪的致病特点是","discription":"风邪的致病特点是：风为百病之长；风为阳邪，其性开泄，易袭阳位；风性善行数变；风性主动。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggswj_ay_2255_201407","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"B","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"易袭阳位","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"易扰神志","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"易耗气","fourth":"易伤津液","answerPic":"","first":"易袭阴位"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"具有强烈传染性的外感病邪是","discription":"疫疠是一类具有强烈传染性的外感病邪，具有发病急骤、病情危重、症状相似、传染性强、易于流行的特点。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggswj_ay_2256_201407","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"A","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"痰饮","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"瘀血","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"六气","fourth":"六淫","answerPic":"","first":"疫疠"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"下列哪项小是中医四诊的内容","discription":"四诊是中医诊察疾病、收集病情资料的基本方法，包括望、闻、问、切。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggswj_ay_2257_201407","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"A",